  m_text: '1. Purpose of the Simulation

    The simulation is intended to provide
    you with a realistic overview of various professions, helping you understand
    the typical tasks, challenges, and responsibilities associated with different
    career paths. By engaging in this simulation, you acknowledge that the experience
    is designed for educational and career exploration purposes only.



    2. Data
    Collection and Usage

    We will collect both behavioral data (how you interact
    with the game, your choices, time spent on tasks, etc.) and feedback data (through
    surveys or questionnaires) during and after the simulation. The data will be
    used for the following purposes:

